description: Stuck for school lunch ideas? Add colour to the kids' lunch boxes with this easy poached chicken rice paper rolls recipe. Approved by nutritionists, adored by kids.
name: Rice Paper Roll Lunch Box Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Place rolls in lunch boxes along with ricotta spooned into 2 small airtight containers, crispbreads and apple.
